title: count_maildir()
brief: Count the number of maildirs.
----


<p>When in maildir mode, set with <a href="global_mode.html">global_mode</a>, the user interface consists of a list of maildir folders.</p>
<p>This function will count the number of visible maildirs.</p>
<p class="seealso">See also <a href="current_maildir.html">current_maildir()</a>, <a href="selected_folders.html">selected_folders()</a>.</p>
